OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774857950
OL,3,CNASA's Artemis II astronauts arrive at
OL,4,CFlorida launch site for moon trip
OL,6,FThe mission will see the crew travel
OL,7,Ffurther from Earth than any other
OL,8,Fhuman, ITV News Science Correspondent
OL,9,FMartin Stew reports
OL,11,FThe rocket is ready, the astronauts
OL,12,Fsay they are ready and, by Wednesday,
OL,13,Fthey could be off.
OL,15,FThe crew of Artemis II, the first
OL,16,Flunar mission in more than fifty
OL,17,Fyears, arrived at the Kennedy Space
OL,18,FCenter on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
