OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774857950
OL,3,CNASA's Artemis II astronauts arrive at
OL,4,CFlorida launch site for moon trip
OL,6,FThey are: commander Reid Wiseman,
OL,7,Fpilot Victor Glover, and mission
OL,8,Fspecialists Christina Cook and Jeremy
OL,9,FHansen.
OL,11,FThey themselves won't be setting foot
OL,12,Fon the moon but it's hoped their 10-
OL,13,Fday flight will prove surface
OL,14,Fexploration is not far away.
OL,16,FMission specialist Christina Cook has
OL,17,Fspent 11 months in orbit before,
OL,18,Ftaking part in the first all female
OL,19,Fspace walk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
