PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774857950
OL,3,CNASA's Artemis II astronauts arrive at
OL,4,CFlorida launch site for moon trip
OL,6,F"There are definitely going to be
OL,7,Fthings by day 6, 7, 8, 9 that we're
OL,8,Flike, man, all right, I need a little
OL,9,Fspace and I can't get any right now.
OL,10,FBut we are a good crew."
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FOnly 24 humans have travelled to the
OL,18,Fmoon and back, the last leaving 53
OL,19,Fyears ago. But this team is different.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
