PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774857950
OL,3,CNASA's Artemis II astronauts arrive at
OL,4,CFlorida launch site for moon trip
OL,6,FSpace Scientist Dame Maggie Aderin
OL,7,Fsaid: "They were all white, all
OL,8,FAmerican and all male.
OL,10,F"Artemis intends to get the first
OL,11,FAmerican to the moon, the first person
OL,12,Fof a different ethnicity and the first
OL,13,Fnon-American to the moon so it is
OL,14,Fquite a magical moment in many ways
OL,15,Fand I'm really excited by this."
OL,17,FPilot Victor Glover said: "I actually
OL,18,Fspend a lot of time keeping myself
OL,19,Ffrom thinking beyond the mission on
OL,20,Fpurpose.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
