PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774857950
OL,3,CNASA's Artemis II astronauts arrive at
OL,4,CFlorida launch site for moon trip
OL,6,F"When I start to daydream about those
OL,7,Fthings just because I really want to
OL,8,Ffocus and give my all to this, this
OL,9,Ftask."
OL,11,FAt 10 days this trip will be shorter
OL,12,Fin time but will the crew travel
OL,13,Ffurther from Earth than any other
OL,14,Fhuman.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
